This is my first mg map,its de_dust themed and the objective for Ts is to get to the buttons and press them before the CTs kill them,and if the Ts do end up pressing the button,they get revenge by grabbing either an ak47 or an m4a1 and shoot them while their stuck inside of a glass dome.
